<lb ed="C I" n="0233a00"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 87</head>
<lb ed="C I" n="0233a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>棲閑寺邑義六十人造像記</title></jhead></juan>
<lb ed="C I" n="0233a01"/><p id="pI01p0233a0101">夫理寂虛凝。非浮情所側。假形名相。會趣消氓。邑義□□□□□□□□
<lb ed="C I" n="0233a02"/>十人等。萇悲二<note n="0233001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30889;＝鼠【史】</note><app n="0233001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鼠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30889;</rdg></app>交侵。形從電逝。夙霄涕慕。仰戀真容。心同歸□□□□
<lb ed="C I" n="0233a03"/>寶。遂割&CB08824;糊口。捨服履寒。共在棲閑寺敬造石碑像一軀。上為皇<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">帝</unclear>□□。
<lb ed="C I" n="0233a04"/>下及三塗。其像也。石勝京山。匠巧般倕。相<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">脫</unclear>真儀。妙過世有。聞之者。望風
<lb ed="C I" n="0233a05"/>如迴首。<note n="0233002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00418;＝睹【史】</note><app n="0233002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">睹</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00418;</rdg></app>之者。肅敬如踟躕。其地土號瑯琊。帝室遺居。前距高崗。卻背金
<lb ed="C I" n="0233a06"/>墉。左帶萇沂。右<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">俠</unclear>山峰。寺則林同玄菀。下若遊仙。端<note n="0233003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB03163;＝坐【史】</note><app n="0233003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">坐</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB03163;</rdg></app>獨念。叡智通神。邑
<lb ed="C I" n="0233a07"/>義等。並識<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">達</unclear>玄宗。妙<note n="0233004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00362;＝體【史】</note><app n="0233004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">體</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00362;</rdg></app>空寂。敦崇三寶。於茲日益。其辭曰。
<lb ed="C I" n="0233a08"/>微微能絕。顯著滿空。含生等潤。不言如功。
<lb ed="C I" n="0233a09"/>慕仰雙林。圖鏤真容。<app source="0233002" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">睹</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00418;</rdg></app>茲妙相。夙夜乾恭。
<lb ed="C I" n="0233a10"/>陰陽迭<note n="0233005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31081;＝布【史】</note><app n="0233005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">布</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31081;</rdg></app>。物故虧盈。悲同彫落。刊石留名。　　司州汲　郡尚孝舉之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">辭</unclear>□。
<lb ed="C I" n="0233a11"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">大</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">齊</unclear>天統五年歲次己丑九月丁亥朔十四□□卯。邑義六十人等之碑頌。</p>
